textfsm_template:
Value ICMP_SEQ (\d+)
Value TTL (\d+)
Value TIME (\d+\.\d+)
Value PACKETS_TRANSMITTED (\d+)
Value PACKETS_RECEIVED (\d+)
Value PACKET_LOSS (\d+)
Value RTT_MIN (\d+\.\d+)
Value RTT_AVG (\d+\.\d+)
Value RTT_MAX (\d+\.\d+)

Start
  ^64 bytes from \d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+: icmp_seq=${ICMP_SEQ} ttl=${TTL} time=${TIME} ms -> Record
  ^--- \d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+ ping statistics ---
  ^${PACKETS_TRANSMITTED} packets transmitted, ${PACKETS_RECEIVED} received, ${PACKET_LOSS}% packet loss
  ^rtt min/avg/max/mdev = ${RTT_MIN}/${RTT_AVG}/${RTT_MAX}/\d+\.\d+ ms
